prompt.content: Let G be an undirected graph with edge set {(49,13), (23,28), (46,35), (32,42), (35,32), (42,22), (13,23), (46,49)}. Find a path from vertex 46 to vertex 22. Express your final answer in the form \boxed{v1,v2,...,vk}, where each vertex is separated by a comma.
